---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Indian Restaurant Near Williams, AZ — Spice Grill & Bar (~18 Miles West via I-40)"
  description="Spice Grill & Bar is about 18 miles west of Williams, AZ via I-40 Exit 146 — roughly 18 minutes. Authentic Punjabi Indian cuisine on historic Route 66."
  ogTitle="Indian Restaurant Near Williams, AZ — Spice Grill & Bar"
  ogDescription="About 18 miles west of Williams, AZ. Authentic Punjabi cuisine at I-40 Exit 146 in Ash Fork, AZ."
>
  <main class="pt-32 pb-24 px-6 bg-surface-container-lowest min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Answer-first H1 -->
      <h1 class="speakable-heading text-[1.875rem] md:text-display-md text-on-surface mb-6">
        Spice Grill &amp; Bar —
        <span class="text-primary-container">About 18 Miles West of Williams, AZ</span>
      </h1>

      <!-- Lead paragraph: direct extractable answer -->
      <p class="speakable-lead text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-6">
        Spice Grill &amp; Bar is located in Ash Fork, Arizona, about 18 miles west of Williams via
        I-40 West — roughly 18 minutes to Exit 146. It is the closest Indian restaurant to Williams
        and Kaibab Estates West on the I-40 corridor.
      </p>

      <!-- Standalone I-40 Exit 146 sentence for voice extraction -->
      <p class="text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-12">
        Spice Grill &amp; Bar is located at I-40 Exit 146 in Ash Fork, Arizona.
      </p>

      <!-- Why Stop Here section -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-heading-lg text-on-surface mb-6">Why Stop Here</h2>
        <div class="bg-surface-container p-8 rounded-2xl">
          <p class="text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant">
            Spice Grill &amp; Bar is the closest authentic Indian restaurant to Williams, the
            gateway to the Grand Canyon Railway, and to Kaibab Estates West, a residential community
            about 5 miles north of Ash Fork. Whether you're catching the train to the Canyon or live
            nearby, our tandoor cooking and freshly baked naan are about 18 minutes east on I-40
            Exit 146.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Distance from Nearby Cities section -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-heading-lg text-on-surface mb-6">Distance from Nearby Cities</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <p class="text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant">
            Spice Grill &amp; Bar is about 18 miles from Williams, AZ — about 18 minutes west on
            I-40. Take Exit 146 in Ash Fork.
          </p>
          <p class="text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant">
            Spice Grill &amp; Bar is about 5 miles from Kaibab Estates West — about 6 minutes south
            via local roads to Ash Fork. Kaibab Estates West sits north of Ash Fork, off the I-40
            corridor.
          </p>
          <p class="text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant">
            Spice Grill &amp; Bar is about 78 miles from the Grand Canyon South Rim — about 1 hour
            20 minutes via AZ-64 South and I-40. Take Exit 146 in Ash Fork.
          </p>
          <p class="text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant">
            Spice Grill &amp; Bar is about 51 miles from Flagstaff, AZ — about 46 minutes west on
            I-40. Take Exit 146 in Ash Fork.
          </p>
          <p class="text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant">
            Spice Grill &amp; Bar is about 25 miles from Seligman, AZ — about 24 minutes east on
            I-40. Take Exit 146 in Ash Fork.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- What to Order section -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-heading-lg text-on-surface mb-6">What to Order</h2>
        <p class="text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-6">
          We recommend these popular dishes for travelers stopping in from the road.
        </p>
        <div class="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2">
          <div class="bg-surface-container p-6 rounded-2xl">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-2">
              <h3 class="text-heading-md text-on-surface">Fish Pakora</h3>
              <span class="text-primary-container font-semibold">$11.99</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Marinated fish fried in crispy chickpea batter — a road-trip crowd favorite.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface-container p-6 rounded-2xl">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-2">
              <h3 class="text-heading-md text-on-surface">Butter Chicken</h3>
              <span class="text-primary-container font-semibold">$17.99</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Rich butter-cream and tomato sauce with tender chicken thighs.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface-container p-6 rounded-2xl">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-2">
              <h3 class="text-heading-md text-on-surface">Shahi Paneer</h3>
              <span class="text-primary-container font-semibold">$16.99</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Cottage cheese in savory buttery cream sauce — a vegetarian favorite.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-surface-container p-6 rounded-2xl">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-2">
              <h3 class="text-heading-md text-on-surface">Chicken Biryani</h3>
              <span class="text-primary-container font-semibold">$18.99</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Fragrant basmati rice sautéed with chicken and aromatic spices.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="bg-surface-container p-6 rounded-2xl sm:col-span-2 sm:max-w-sm sm:mx-auto w-full"
          >
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-2">
              <h3 class="text-heading-md text-on-surface">Garlic Naan</h3>
              <span class="text-primary-container font-semibold">$4.99</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Freshly baked and drizzled with butter and garlic.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Operating Hours (standalone paragraph for voice extraction) -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-heading-lg text-on-surface mb-6">Hours</h2>
        <p class="speakable-hours text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant">
          Spice Grill &amp; Bar is open Monday through Thursday from 8 AM to 9 PM, and Friday
          through Sunday from 8 AM to 10 PM.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Cross-links section with keyword-rich anchor text -->
      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-heading-lg text-on-surface mb-6">Plan Your Visit</h2>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
          <a
            href="/directions/"
            class="inline-block bg-primary-container text-on-primary-container font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-primary-container/90 transition-colors text-center"
          >
            Driving directions to Spice Grill &amp; Bar from 7 cities
          </a>
          <a
            href="/"
            class="inline-block bg-surface-container text-on-surface font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors text-center"
          >
            View the full Spice Grill &amp; Bar menu
          </a>
          <a
            href="/faq/"
            class="inline-block bg-surface-container text-on-surface font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-surface-container-high transition-colors text-center"
          >
            Frequently asked questions about Spice Grill &amp; Bar
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <!-- Page-specific inline FAQ schema (separate from global FAQSchema) -->
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "FAQPage",
      "mainEntity": [
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "How far is Spice Grill & Bar from Williams, AZ?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Spice Grill & Bar is about 18 miles west of Williams, AZ on I-40 — roughly 18 minutes. Take Exit 146 in Ash Fork. We are the closest Indian restaurant to Williams along the I-40 corridor."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Is there an Indian restaurant near Kaibab Estates West?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Yes. Spice Grill & Bar is about 5 miles south of Kaibab Estates West in Ash Fork, AZ — roughly 6 minutes by car. We are the closest sit-down Indian restaurant to the community."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "What is the best Indian restaurant near Williams, AZ on I-40?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Spice Grill & Bar — at I-40 Exit 146 in Ash Fork — is the closest authentic Punjabi restaurant to Williams. About 18 miles west, 18 minutes via I-40. Tandoor cooking, fresh naan, full bar."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  </script>

  <!-- Speakable schema markup -->
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "WebPage",
      "name": "Indian Restaurant Near Williams, AZ",
      "speakable": {
        "@type": "SpeakableSpecification",
        "cssSelector": [".speakable-heading", ".speakable-lead", ".speakable-hours"]
      }
    }
  </script>
</Layout>
